  "quality_gates": {
    "code_coverage": ">=85%",
    "performance_budget": "<100ms p95 API response time",
    "security_checks": [
      "Input validation (Zod)",
      "Password hashing (bcrypt/argon2 via Lucia)",
      "Rate limiting",
      "CORS configuration",
      "OWASP Top 10 compliance"
    ]
  },
  "notes": "This plan is focused on secure, scalable, and maintainable email/password authentication. Lucia Auth is used for modern, type-safe session management. All input is validated with Zod. Passwords are hashed securely. The architecture is modular and testable, following Clean Architecture and DDD principles. All endpoints are covered by unit, integration, and e2e tests. Monitoring and CI/CD are included for production readiness."
